    <recordLookups>
        <description>Some customers are delayed in being canceled in JG until they are removed from the larger Org or refunded. During this waiting period, they do not have a future cancellation date, which can trigger the automation to incorrectly switch their type back to Customer. To prevent this, if the latest case is a cancellation request with a JG Cancellation Status of &apos;Pending - Waiting on Site Removal&apos; or &apos;Pending - Waiting on Refund,&apos; the account type should not be changed back to Customer.</description>
        <name>Get_Latest_Opened_Case</name>
        <label>Get Latest Opened Case</label>
        <locationX>50</locationX>
        <locationY>1152</locationY>
        <assignNullValuesIfNoRecordsFound>false</assignNullValuesIfNoRecordsFound>
        <connector>
